author: @alonsoquijano6749
text: I did my bachelor in Economics and I had always been good at math. Then, I suddenly quit my job and went abroad to study music professionally. I did a master's in music in China. Now, I am preparing for a PhD in Economics and many think my background in music has ruined my career... Love passion for music and mathematics makes me happy :)

author: @maxfeng4532

Looking forward to more STAT videos(a life saver for me and my bioinformatic friends), new songs and cats!
